# Privacy Policy for [APP_NAME]

**Last Updated: [DATE_TO_BE_FILLED]**

## Overview

[APP_NAME] ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application [APP_NAME].

## Information We Collect

### Information You Provide
- **Account Information**: Username, email address, and authentication credentials
- **Configuration Data**: AI agent configurations, prompts, and templates you create
- **API Keys**: Third-party service API keys (stored encrypted)
- **Usage Preferences**: App settings and customization preferences

### Automatically Collected Information
- **Device Information**: Device type, operating system, app version
- **Usage Analytics**: App usage patterns, feature utilization, performance metrics
- **Log Data**: Error logs, execution logs, and diagnostic information

### Third-Party Service Data
- **AI Provider APIs**: Data sent to and received from AI services (OpenAI, Google, Anthropic, etc.)
- **Authentication Services**: Data from third-party authentication providers if used

## How We Use Your Information

We use the collected information to:
- Provide and maintain the [APP_NAME] service
- Execute AI agents and process your requests
- Improve app functionality and user experience
- Provide customer support and technical assistance
- Ensure security and prevent unauthorized access
- Comply with legal obligations

## Data Storage and Security

### Encryption
- All API keys are encrypted using industry-standard encryption
- Data transmission uses HTTPS/TLS encryption
- Local data storage uses device-level encryption when available

### Data Retention
- Account data: Retained while your account is active
- Usage logs: Retained for 90 days for diagnostic purposes
- AI execution data: Retained for 30 days unless deleted sooner

### Third-Party Services
- AI providers (Google Gemini, OpenAI, etc.) have their own privacy policies
- We do not store or log the content of your AI interactions
- API calls are made directly from your device to AI providers

## Data Sharing and Disclosure

We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties except:
- **AI Service Providers**: To execute your AI agents (as directed by you)
- **Legal Requirements**: When required by law or to protect our rights
- **Service Providers**: Trusted partners who assist in app operation (under strict confidentiality)

## Your Rights and Choices

You have the right to:
- Access your personal information
- Correct inaccurate information
- Delete your account and associated data
- Export your configuration data
- Opt-out of analytics (where technically feasible)

## Children's Privacy

[APP_NAME] is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.

## International Data Transfers

Your information may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your own. We ensure appropriate safeguards are in place for such transfers.

## Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you of significant changes through the app or by email.

## Contact Information

For privacy-related questions or concerns:
- Email: [PRIVACY_EMAIL_TO_BE_FILLED]
- Address: [COMPANY_ADDRESS_TO_BE_FILLED]

## Platform-Specific Information

### iOS-Specific Disclosures
- **Camera**: Used for QR code scanning (configuration import/export)
- **Microphone**: Used for voice commands (if enabled)
- **Location**: Used for location-based AI services (optional)

### Android-Specific Disclosures
- **Internet Permission**: Required for AI service communication
- **Camera Permission**: Optional, for QR code scanning
- **Microphone Permission**: Optional, for voice features
- **Location Permission**: Optional, for location-based services

## Data Processing Legal Basis (GDPR)

For EU users, we process your data based on:
- **Contract**: To provide the [APP_NAME] service
- **Legitimate Interest**: To improve our service and ensure security
- **Consent**: For optional features like analytics and marketing communications

